msgid "Metadata management"
msgstr "元数据管理"

msgid ""
"Categories are typically a concept, for example \"Gender\", \"Age\" or "
"\"Disease Status\". Use categories to disaggregate data elements into "
"individual components. You can also use category combinations to assign "
"metadata attributes to all data recorded in a specific dataset."
msgstr ""
"类别通常是一个概念，例如 \"性别\"、\"年龄 \"或 "
"\"疾病状态\"。使用类别可将数据元素分解为单个组件。您还可以使用类别组合为特定数据集中记录的所有数据分配元数据属性。"

msgid "Individual values or options that can be selected within a category."
msgstr "可在一个类别中选择的单个值或选项。"

msgid "Disaggregate data elements into individual components."
msgstr "将数据元素分解为各个组成部分。"

msgid ""
"Combine multiple categories into a related set that can be assigned to data "
"elements for dissagregation. Can also be used to to assign metadata "
"attributes to data sets or programs."
msgstr "将多个类别组合成一个相关的集合，可分配给数据元素进行分解。也可用于为数据集或程序分配元数据属性。"

msgid ""
"Specify code and attributes to enable easier data exchange with other "
"systems."
msgstr "指定代码和属性，以便于与其他系统进行数据交换。"

msgid ""
"Group category options and improve analysis with category option group sets."
msgstr "将类别选项分组，利用类别选项分组集改进分析。"

msgid ""
"Classify category options groups to add more dimensionality to captured data"
" for analysis."
msgstr "对类别选项组进行分类，为获取的数据增加更多维度进行分析。"

msgid "Data Approval"
msgstr "数据审核"

msgid ""
"Data approval workflows create a process for authorized users to review and "
"approve data at specified levels."
msgstr "数据审批工作流为授权用户创建了一个在指定级别审查和审批数据的流程。"

msgid "Configure data approval levels for use in data approval workflows."
msgstr "配置数据审批级别，以便在数据审批工作流程中使用。"

msgid "Configure data approval workflows."
msgstr "配置数据审批工作流程。"

msgid ""
"Data elements are fundamental units for data collection in DHIS2, "
"representing individual data points for both tracker and aggregate data. "
"They serve as the building blocks for capturing, analysing, and reporting "
"information."
msgstr "数据元素是 DHIS2 数据收集的基本单位，代表跟踪数据和汇总数据的单个数据点。它们是获取、分析和报告信息的基础模块。"

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete data elements: the foundation of data "
"collection and analysis."
msgstr "创建、更新、查看和删除数据元素：数据收集和分析的基础。"

msgid ""
"Improve analysis of single data elements by combining them into data element"
" groups."
msgstr "通过将单一数据元素合并为数据元素组，改进对这些数据元素的分析。"

msgid ""
"Add another level of organisation by grouping data element groups into group"
" sets."
msgstr "通过将数据元素组归入组集，增加另一个组织层次。"

msgid ""
"Data sets are collections of data elements grouped for aggregate data entry,"
" validation, access, collection frequency and reporting. Data entry forms "
"are defined and configured by data sets. They help streamline the management"
" of data collection routines and ensure consistency across different stages "
"of data handling within DHIS2."
msgstr ""
"数据集是数据元素的集合，用于汇总数据录入、验证、访问、收集频率和报告。数据输入表格由数据集定义和配置。它们有助于简化数据收集程序的管理，并确保 "
"DHIS2 系统内不同数据处理阶段的一致性。"

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete data sets, specify the related data "
"elements, period type organisation units, sharing settings and workflow "
"approval here."
msgstr "在此创建、更新、查看和删除数据集，指定相关数据元素、周期类型组织单位、共享设置和工作流程审批。"

msgid "Create, update, view and delete data set notification templates."
msgstr "创建、更新、查看和删除数据集通知模板。"

msgid ""
"Indicators are used to calculate and analyze data based on data elements and"
" other indicators. Predictors are used to predict future data values."
msgstr "指标用于根据数据元素和其他指标计算和分析数据。预测器用于预测未来的数据值。"

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete indicators, specify the numerator and "
"denominator, and set the indicator type."
msgstr "创建、更新、查看和删除指标，指定分子和分母，并设置指标类型。"

msgid ""
"Create, modify, view and delete indicator types. An indicator type is a "
"factor for an indicator, like percentage."
msgstr "创建、更改、查看和删除指标类型，指标类型是一个指标的一个因子，如百分比"

msgid ""
"Create, modify, view and delete indicator groups. Groups are used for "
"improved analysis."
msgstr "创建、修改、查看和删除指标组，该组被用于提高数据分析。"

msgid ""
"Create, modify, view and delete indicator group sets. Group sets are used "
"for improved analysis."
msgstr "创建、更改、查看和删除组集，该组集被用于提高数据分析"

msgid ""
"Create, update, view and delete program indicators, define expressions and "
"filters, and configure analytics settings."
msgstr "创建、更新、查看和删除程序指标，定义表达式和过滤器，配置分析设置。"

msgid "Group program indicators for easier analysis."
msgstr "将计划指标分组，以便于分析。"

msgid "Create predictors which can be used to predict future data values."
msgstr "创建根据过去的期间生成预测将来的数据值的预测器。"

msgid "Create predictor groups that contain several related predictors."
msgstr "创建包含多个相关预测因子的预测因子组。"

msgid "Option sets are used to limit data entry to defined values."
msgstr "选项集用于将数据输入限制在定义的值范围内。"

msgid ""
"Create option sets which can be included in data elements and produce drop-"
"down lists in data entry forms."
msgstr "创建可以被数据元包括的值域选项集，并可用在数据录入表单中生成下拉选项"

msgid ""
"Create a group of options from option sets that has a similar functional "
"area or meaning."
msgstr "从功能区或含义相似的选项集中创建一个选项组。"

msgid "Create, modify and view sets of option groups."
msgstr "创建、修改和查看选项组。"

msgid ""
"Organisation units are the structural entities within DHIS2 that define "
"locations or points of service where data is collected. Examples include "
"regions, hospitals, clinics, or departments. They help establish the "
"hierarchy and scope for data access, collection, reporting, and analysis. "
"Organisation units can be organised into groups and group sets."
msgstr ""
"组织单位是 DHIS2 "
"中的结构实体，定义了收集数据的地点或服务点。例如地区、医院、诊所或部门。它们有助于建立数据访问、收集、报告和分析的层次和范围。组织单位可分为组和组集。"

msgid "Create, update, view and delete individual organisation units."
msgstr "创建、更新、查看和删除单个组织单位。"

msgid ""
"Categorise similar organisation units into groups, like hospitals or "
"clinics, enabling efficient data aggregation and analysis across diverse "
"locations in DHIS2."
msgstr "将类似的组织单位分类，如医院或诊所，以便在 DHIS2 中有效地汇总和分析不同地点的数据。"

msgid ""
"Organise multiple groups with shared characteristics into sets, allowing for"
" another level of data analysis and comparison across the organisation "
"structure."
msgstr "将具有共同特征的多个小组组织成组，以便在整个组织结构中进行另一层次的数据分析和比较。"

msgid ""
"Organisation unit levels define hierarchical layers within the organisation "
"structure, such as national or regional tiers, and specify the names used "
"for each level."
msgstr "组织单位级别定义了组织结构中的层次，如国家或地区层级，并指定了每个级别的名称。"

msgid "Placeholder for other"
msgstr "其他"

msgid "Upload, modify and view icons which can be assigned to other metadata."
msgstr "上传、修改和查看可分配给其他元数据的图标。"

msgid "Create, modify and view attributes."
msgstr "创建和更新动态属性。属性可以用于数据元、指标、机构和用户。"

msgid ""
"Create constants which can be included in expressions of indicator and "
"validation rules."
msgstr "创建可用于指标和验证表达式的常数"

msgid "Configure external map layers for use in GIS."
msgstr "配置Gis中使用的外部图层。"

msgid ""
"Create, modify and view predefined legends for maps and other "
"visualisations."
msgstr "创建、修改和查看地图预定义的图例和其它可视化属性。"

msgid ""
"Create and manage locales for database content. A locale is a combination of"
" language and country."
msgstr "创建和管理数据库方言，国家和语言的组合。"

msgid ""
"Manage analytics to be emailed to specific user groups on a daily, weekly or"
" monthly basis."
msgstr "管理每天、每周或每月通过邮件进行的分析推送。"

msgid "Configure hooks in SQL that run during the analytics process."
msgstr "在 SQL 中配置在分析过程中运行的钩子。"

msgid ""
"Create SQL database views, typically based on resource tables, to provide "
"convenient views for third-party tools."
msgstr "创建 SQL 数据库视图（通常基于资源表），为第三方工具提供方便的视图。"

msgid ""
"Programs are used to collect, manage, and analyze event-based and "
"longitudinal data. They allow you to define program stages, track entities "
"such as people or items over time, and apply rules and relationships to "
"support flexible data capture and analysis."
msgstr ""
"程序用于收集、管理和分析基于事件的数据和纵向数据。程序允许您定义程序阶段，随时间跟踪实体（如人或物品），并应用规则和关系来支持灵活的数据采集和分析。"

msgid ""
"Create, modify and view programs. A program has program stages and defines "
"which actions should be taken at each stage."
msgstr "创建、修改和浏览项目，一个项目有多个项目阶段，并且定义了每一个阶段该做什么。"

msgid ""
"Create, modify and view tracked entity attributes. An attribute can be used "
"to register extra information for a tracked entity."
